    <item>
      <title>拜登团队公布与特朗普辩论相关的 5000 万美元广告宣传活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/biden-team-unveils-50-million-ad-campaign-tied-to-trump-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的连任竞选活动正在启动一项耗资 5000 万美元的 6 月广告宣传活动，目标是在下周与唐纳德·特朗普进行辩论之前，瞄准战场州的少数族裔选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/biden-team-unveils-50-million-ad-campaign-tied-to-trump-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中韩即将举行 2015 年以来首次安全会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-south-korea-set-for-their-first-security-talks-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和韩国将举行约九年来首次高层安全会谈，预计此次在首尔举行的会谈将与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京自 2000 年以来首次访问朝鲜同时进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-south-korea-set-for-their-first-security-talks-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 08:45:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度火车相撞至少造成 8 人死亡，数十人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-trains-collide-in-eastern-india-killing-at-least-5-with-rescue-work-ongoing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新德里（美联社）——官员称，周一，一列货运列车与一列客运列车在印度东部西孟加拉邦相撞，造成至少 8 人死亡，数人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-trains-collide-in-eastern-india-killing-at-least-5-with-rescue-work-ongoing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 05:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
