    <item>
      <title>中国指责菲律宾船只在南海与中国船只相撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-china-says-a-chinese-vessel-and-philippine-supply-ship-collided-in-the-disputed-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台北（美联社）——中国海岸警卫队称，一艘中国船只与一艘菲律宾补给船于周一在南海有争议的斯普拉特利群岛附近发生碰撞，这是领土争端不断升级并引发警觉的最新一次爆发。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-china-says-a-chinese-vessel-and-philippine-supply-ship-collided-in-the-disputed-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:17:57 GMT</pubDate>
